      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, a masterpiece of naturally aspirated engineering delivering 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline. This example boasts a 6-speed manual transmission with precise gate engagement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is unparalleled, featuring the weight-saving carbon fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof to lower the center of gravity. Meticulously maintained, the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014critical components for this platform\u2014have been proactively addressed with documented service history. The Alpine White finish retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or road rash, while the Novillo leather interior shows no compression or bolster wear. Mechanically, the vehicle is turn-key, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a dry undercarriage free of fluid seepage. An investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
